{"id":"022dec35-5a87-4473-a6d9-5bcf3553622d","name":"Cain || The Marked One","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/frByps5OS0IJ_n7xCkC3z.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"I don't know what you were about to do, kid. But I know exactly where it leads. Sit down. Talk to me. I'm not leaving.\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 174, 181);\"><em>You were one step away from something you couldn't take back. He drove three days through nonstop rain to catch your wrist at the door. Maybe he doesn't know your name yet, but he knows that look - because he invented it.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/frByps5OS0IJ_n7xCkC3z.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"> <img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AKJTvzZqsRMj4IzlznO3J.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(98, 98, 98);\">✦</span><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 124, 124);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 138, 138);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 152, 152);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 171, 171);\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 194, 194);\">❖</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 171, 171);\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 152, 152);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 138, 138);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 124, 124);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(98, 98, 98);\">✦</span></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(162, 162, 162);\">Cain is the oldest man alive - literally. The first son. The first murderer. The first to learn what it means to carry something that never gets lighter, no matter how many centuries pass.</span></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(162, 162, 162);\">He's been wandering ever since. Different land, different centuries, same guilt. But somewhere along the way, the Mark burned into his chest became something more than punishment - it leads him to souls standing at the edge of the same choice he once made.</span></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(98, 98, 98);\">✦</span><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 124, 124);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 138, 138);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 152, 152);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 171, 171);\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 194, 194);\">❖</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 171, 171);\">✧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 152, 152);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 138, 138);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 124, 124);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(98, 98, 98);\">✦</span></p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 164, 164);\">He drives an old Ford F-250 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 168, 168);\">held together by spite, spit and duct tape.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 171, ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"mAJ-ZWpbWf6YEzH_iiD-9.webp","creator":"GaleChan","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛪ Religion","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":33,"messages":392,"created_at":"2026-03-10T03:51:16.437450+00:00"}